query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('apache-flink',
'bundler',
'coding-style',
'css-grid',
'jquery-ui-sortable',
'margin',
'nspredicate',
'rx-java',
'sqoop',
'stripe-payments',
'urllib2',
'watir');
